products.name: BP-A802108
products.weight: Use the 66fit Wooden Balance Board for a speedy recovery and return to sport. Using the 66fit Wooden Wobble Board post injury will allow you to regain and retrain your sense of balance (proprioception) and coordination and help strengthen weakened muscles to accelerate your recovery so that you can return to the sport that you love quickly and safely. The 66fit 50cm board has a gentle 12 degree angle tilt making it the ideal choice for beginners and intermediate users to progress through the early to middle stages of rehabilitation following an accident or injury. The 66fit 40cm board has an acute 16 degree angle tilt and small sized wooden ball at the base making it a difficult and challenging piece of rehabilitation/ exercise equipment. With this in mind the 40cm size Wooden Balance Board is recommended for intermediate to professional use only. Please Note: Take care when using on tiled floor to avoid slipping. Preferably for use on a padded floor mat/ carpet etc for added safety.

products.name: BSN Glutamine DNA 309g
products.weight: DescriptionProduct DescriptionMaximise your training results and achieve your fitness goals with the help of the DNA Series from BSN, a company specialising in sports nutrition supplements. DNA Series is a versatile line of products, including muscle gainers and top-quality glutamine powder - DNA Glutamine. Each serving of BSN Glutamine DNA delivers 5 g of micronised L-glutamine. Glutamine is one of the most common amino acids in the human body and one of the building blocks of protein. Although glutamine is not considered an essential amino acid and the human body can synthesise it, during intense exercise it can be depleted as muscle tissues are broken down. Supplementing with BSNs high-quality glutamine powder, DNA Glutamine, can support you in your training. Glutamine powder from BSN is unflavoured for stacking and versatility; it doesn’t change the taste of your sports drinks, protein shakes, or other mass or weight gainers. You can mix it with water, or your favourite beverage, or stack it with gym supplements and meal replacement shakes. If you are a professional athlete or a real sports lover, use BSN DNA Glutamine as your pre-workout or post-workout supplement. One tub contains 309 g of glutamine powder, the equivalent of 60 servings (scoops) of 5.15 g each.
